dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Nathan Taylor. May I have your name, please?
Hi Nathan, my name is Marilyn Anderson.
Nice to meet you, Marilyn. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's three two five six seven.
Thank you. Additionally, could you provide me with your date of birth for verification purposes?
My date of birth is zero two one five one nine seven eight.
Great, thank you for that information, Marilyn. How can I assist you today with Old Stone Auto Insurance?
I would like to inquire about adding another vehicle to my policy.
Certainly, Marilyn. Let's go over the details. What is the make and model of the vehicle you want to add?
Thank you for your time, Marilyn. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
